high_descs: go to the bedroom and stand in front of the bed.
Pick the knife up from the bed.
look at the lettuce.
go over to the lettuce and cut it using the knife.
walk to the diningtable in the living room.
Put down the knife on the diningtable.
go back into the bed.
pick up a piece of the lettuce.
Take the fruit to the fridge in the kitchen.
Put the lettuce in the storage cabinet then remove it.
take the fruit to the diningtable in the living room.
Put the lettuce down on the diningtable next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Get some lettuce and put it on the dining table.

high_descs: Exit this room through the door ahead and to the right, turning left into the hallway and taking the left into the bedroom, approaching the bed.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Approach the lettuce at the head of the bed.
Cut the lettuce up.
Exit this room the way you came in, then turn right and go down the hall all the way until reaching the living room, turning right towards the TV then left towards the diningtable.
Place the knife down on the diningtable.
Return to the bed with the cut up lettuce.
Pick up the lettuce.
Exit the room the way you came in, go back down the hallway and turn left into the kitchen area, approaching the fridge.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge then take the lettuce out.
Turn around and head back to the diningtable you placed the knife down on.
Put the lettuce down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a cut and cooled piece of lettuce on a diningtable.

high_descs: Turn right, exit the room, go left to room on the left and go to the bed.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Move further to the right of the lettuce.
Slice the lettuce on the bed.
Turn, exit the room, go right down the hall, turn right and go to the white diningtable.
Place the knife on the diningtable.
Turn around, go down the hall and back to the bed in the last room on the left.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left, exit the room, go right down the hall and then left to the fridge.
Place the lettuce on the shelf in the fridge, shut the fridge and then pick up the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn around and go across the room to the white diningtable.
Place the lettuce on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold lettuce slice on the white DiningTable.
